                <h3>Key Points</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>We collect information you provide (account details, reading lists) and usage data</li>
                    <li>We use your information to provide and improve our service</li>
                    <li>We share data with service providers (hosting, SMS delivery) but don't sell your personal information</li>
                    <li>You have control over your data and can request access, correction, or deletion</li>
                    <li>We protect your information with industry-standard security measures</li>
